title: Ocado shares soar on deal with Kroger to enter the U.S.
text:
Ocado shares soar on deal with Kroger to enter the U.S. 11:58am BST - 01:00
Britain's online supermarket Ocado clinched a game-changing deal with Kroger as its exclusive partner in the U.S., securing its entry into the world's biggest market and sending its shares up 50 percent. Jacob Greaves reports.
